{"tid":689083,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"我有螢光JJ","createTime":"2018-06-03T21:13:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T12:18:29.000Z","uid":41791,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9915dd64abc5feec0122acf8a1a9135364ee565d","tid":689083,"uid":41791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T21:13:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/L229QDxDakU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FL229QDxDakU&d=LzoM0JrnwE7uq8%2BNdr6xi54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=aaac0484\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/L229QDxDakU</a><br />\n<br />\n後視鏡裏的世界　越來越遠的道別<br />\n　你轉身向背(北) 側臉還是很美<br />\n　<span style=\"color: red;\">我有螢光JJ</span>　竟聽見著你的淚<br />\n<br />\n在車窗外面徘徊　是我錯失的機會<br />\n　你站的方位　跟我中間隔著淚<br />\n　街景一直在後退　你的崩潰在窗外零碎<br />\n<br />\n我一路向北　離開有你的季節<br />\n　你說你好累　已無法再愛上誰<br />\n　細數慚愧　我傷你幾回<br />\n<br />\n我一路向北　離開有你的季節<br />\n方向盤周圍　回轉著我的後悔<br />\n我加速超越　卻甩不掉緊緊跟隨的傷悲<br />\n細數慚愧　我傷你幾回<br />\n停止狼狽　就讓錯純粹"},{"pid":"e0203546c078bbe0e845657dc27818da0027980f","tid":689083,"uid":171598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T21:13:35.000Z","msg":"i love you"},{"pid":"851aeebf11c18ef1836306593d6db28285e0c2af","tid":689083,"uid":36478,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T21:17:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb1ccbec8a49f441ea879bab27bd63406296b77","tid":689083,"uid":394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T21:18:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e45035b65425b201bc771e186e033cbc7a443fd","tid":689083,"uid":41791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"851aeebf11c18ef1836306593d6db28285e0c2af","tid":689083,"uid":36478,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T21:17:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T21:18:10.000Z